Donabe Rice

2 3/4 cup rice (go)

1:1 water ratio
Rinse rice thoroughly for 1 minute under running water
Finish rinising with a large cup of filtered water
Soak Rice in Donabe in filtered water for 25-30 minutes
Turn heat to medium (5 o clock on the burner)
Cook for 9-11 minutes, watch for steam stream
Watch 30 seconds of steam
turn off
keep lid on, set for 10 minutes
fluff in a bowl and let it cool